{"tid":720821,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"4個半月貓女係咁喵叫","createTime":"2018-06-28T08:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T21:06:59.000Z","uid":189012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e1890ac43ce4f8a3cfd500ae983c7d9da87e5e51","tid":720821,"uid":189012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"本身我隻貓貓就鍾意叫<br />\n但3月中個時感冒左一個月失左聲,失聲時都有叫但出唔到聲<br />\n最近好返又再叫過,但叫得勁左,次數多左,叫耐左大聲左好多<br />\n經常對住屋企門口叫,一係就坐梳化叫,一叫就兩三個鐘叫到訓覺<br />\n有時應佢做乜叫,佢會行埋黎用頭磨手磨頭,輕咬手指同嘴咁,之後行開再叫,不斷loop<br />\n玩下逗貓棒就冇叫,但玩完一陣又叫過<br />\n食就放題肯食,玩就癲晒,勁鍾意通屋走,本身病緊都係咁,好返就更加活躍<br />\n呢兩夜晚訓教同第二朝早6點都會係房門口係咁叫到你訓醒為止<br />\n搞到唔係好夠訓,但始終都唔知佢做乜係咁叫,仲搞到細妹冇叫開既都叫多左<br />\n上網睇過又唔似係發情(4個半月ja wo),又唔係餓,又唔係冇得玩,按摩或者抱一陣又走左去<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多兩日先覆診問到醫生,但就唔似係病,除非貓都有過度活躍症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cbcae300744141b156e7152c64fee809edc504","tid":720821,"uid":30924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"九成係發情....我隻貓 4個月已經生第一胎"},{"pid":"728be90ae4e0be62a6b73ec9db3e4a4cc5b797f7","tid":720821,"uid":30924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a2cbcae300744141b156e7152c64fee809edc504","tid":720821,"uid":30924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"九成係發情....我隻貓 4個月已經生第一胎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"你試下拍下佢屎忽佢爽唔爽...."},{"pid":"bcd2dab76d156ad91ed0c5647ec8b9479d40624c","tid":720821,"uid":189012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2cbcae300744141b156e7152c64fee809edc504","tid":720821,"uid":30924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"九成係發情....我隻貓 4個月已經生第一胎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"咁早就發情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只係見到奶過一次自已gap gap<br />\n不過佢用頭黎磨我隻手指係會訓住係度磨又自轉磨地<br />\n但佢最近病好先得1.8kg,做唔到絕育住,有冇方法可以等佢唔駛叫得咁多"},{"pid":"6a4426d16e8d13edeace2b6f9666b8a918d2f5a4","tid":720821,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"未食飽咪叫囉"},{"pid":"83560e07a3828b9761066908e8eb30c5370e9bb4","tid":720821,"uid":189012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4426d16e8d13edeace2b6f9666b8a918d2f5a4","tid":720821,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"未食飽咪叫囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"放題架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f4f28a2a5b35971760eb5aa75c5665443117fd","tid":720821,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83560e07a3828b9761066908e8eb30c5370e9bb4","tid":720821,"uid":189012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4426d16e8d13edeace2b6f9666b8a918d2f5a4","tid":720821,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"未食飽咪叫囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"放題架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"佢食唔食先？<br />\n<br />\n貓叫通常唔飽"},{"pid":"deb05001d3c2ba1bdd5ddcdc05df5d152b7d1643","tid":720821,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:10:52.000Z","msg":"西痕"},{"pid":"0db3ad915df40917aba3dcdc3e0778cb5cebc601","tid":720821,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"發情lo仲可以係咩"},{"pid":"f1e702466d92aca63322d5781b7a3ef4ba60affe","tid":720821,"uid":189012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72f4f28a2a5b35971760eb5aa75c5665443117fd","tid":720821,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83560e07a3828b9761066908e8eb30c5370e9bb4","tid":720821,"uid":189012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4426d16e8d13edeace2b6f9666b8a918d2f5a4","tid":720821,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dis